Introduction

Queenz Eye is a two-members South Korean girl group under Big Mountain Entertainment.

Originally a six-members girl group, they made their debut on October 24, 2022 with the release of their first single album "Queenz Table".

On April 4, 2023, it was announced through their fancafe that Jenna had departed from Queenz Eye due to personal reasons.

On January 24, 2025, it was reported by their agency that Hannah, Na Rin, and Da Min had left the group.
